                <p>1. Tình yêu Thiên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Chúa như vầng  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>dương soi  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Am7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>tỏa khắp  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>nơi. Tình yêu Thiên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Bb</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Chúa là vì  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>sao giữa đêm mù  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">F</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>tối  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">D7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>.<br>Tình yêu Thiên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Chúa dìu  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>con vượt qua sóng  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Fmaj7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>đời nổi trôi Thuyền con giữa  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>dòng đại dương bấp bênh ngài  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">A7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>ơi.<br>Tình yêu Thiên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Chúa như dòng  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>sông êm  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Am7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>đềm lướt  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>trôi. Chảy xuôi năm  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Bb</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>tháng để hồn  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>thơ tắm trong tình  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">F</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>mến  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">D7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>&nbsp;.<br>Tình yêu Thiên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Chúa nồng  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>say là hương gió  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Fmaj7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>trời dịu êm. Dìu đưa tháng  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>ngày bình yên  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">D7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span> với bao êm  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>đềm.</p>
