r">[</span><span class="chord">C</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>phai dẫu  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Am7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>đời đổi <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span> thay. Nào ai có  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Bb</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>biết tình ngài  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">C7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>luôn sắt son bền vững.<br>Là Chân Thiện  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Mỹ thẳm sâu để con kiếm tìm ngày đêm Hồn con khát  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Gm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>vọng cậy trông  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">D7</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span> vững tin nơi  <span class="chordOC"><span class="chordPer">[</span><span class="chord">Dm</span><span class="chordPer">]</span></span>Ngài</p>
